videos.description: USC's Desiree Caldwell hits the open 3-pointer to give the Trojans a 27-25 lead.

videos.description: Oregon's Cazorla drains the open 3-pointer to give the Ducks a nine-point lead over USC.
videos.headline: Cazorla nails 3-pointer to extend Ducks' lead
